significantly enlarge the class of known exact solutions, while organizing and\nunifying previously discovered solutions in terms of their null structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 May 2013 18:12:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 May 2013 14:51:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 Oct 2013 21:02:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
