 \"super-bubbles\"\n-- outflows that may have broken out of the denser regions of the host galaxy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 May 2013 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2013 16:22:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
