mentations. We apply these\nalgorithms to the strongly correlated Chromium dimer, to demonstrate their\nefficiency and parallelism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 May 2013 00:19:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Jun 2013 16:14:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 26 Jun 2013 13:07:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-10"}
