erns of the shadowing time (scaling\nbehaviors or intermittency patterns) should be a useful means of bio-monitoring\nto detect contaminants in the environment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 May 2013 08:09:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-31"}
